text: Alberto Jara Franzoy (27 July 1929 - 5 September 2019)http://www.iglesia.cl/39035-fallecio-obispo-emerito-de-chillan-alberto- jara-franzoy.html was a Chilean Roman Catholic bishop. Jara Franzoy was born in Chile and was ordained to the priesthood in 1962. He served as bishop of the Roman Catholic Diocese of Chillán, Chile, from 1982 to 2006.Diocese of Chillán ==Notes== Category:1929 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Chilean Roman Catholic bishops
